cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.MM 

The paper deals with a method for improving the performance of decision tree ensembles in the context of face alignment, which is a problem in computer vision. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also introduces a new method for combining decision trees that involves linear regression, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG and cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of quantization, which is a technique used in natural language processing (cs.CL) and computer vision (cs.MM).
